💻 **Credit Card Fraud Risk Analysis Project (GitHub Repository)**

I’m excited to share my **Credit Card Fraud Risk Analysis** project on GitHub! 🚀

This project focuses on detecting fraudulent transactions using data analysis and machine learning techniques. It demonstrates how real-world financial data can be analyzed to identify risks and improve security.

🔍 **Project Features:**
• Data Cleaning & Preprocessing
• Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
• Fraud Detection using Machine Learning Models
• Handling Imbalanced Dataset
• Performance Evaluation of Models
• Interactive Visualizations (Power BI)

